      "397129 -88353 English/French Proficiency Tests",
      "The Client must attain high proficiency in all four areas of their language exam to qualify for the FSWP. The minimum pass mark is six bands in each module or Canadian Language Benchmark (CLB - 7).",
      "Even if the Client meets CLB - 7, they must still earn an overall score high enough to reach 67 points, which is the minimum point requirement to qualify for the FSWP.",
      "If the Client estimated their level of language proficiency in the initial assessment, they acknowledge that DM CONSULTANTS determined their Immigration eligibility based on that estimate.",
      "DM CONSULTANTS shall not be responsible in any manner whatsoever if the Immigration application cannot be submitted because the Client scores below CLB 7(L-6.R-6, W-6, S-6) or falls short of the required 67 points based on language proficiency test results.",
      "To increase the probability of invitation, the Client should try to score CLB9 (L-8, R-7, W-7, S-7) bands in the respective module.",
      "Submit your IELTS or any other language proficiency score card within 90 days of the signing of this Agreement, in order to avoid any delay in the application and lapse of contractual validity.",
      "Additionally, the Client agrees not to sign any forms or documents from government bodies or third parties without prior review and approval by DM. All documentation must be in English or a legally recognized alternate language, accompanied by certified translations.",
