      "Definitions and Interpretation",
      "\"DM Consultants\" shall mean and include all branches, subsidiaries, and affiliates of DM, including, but not limited to, its operations in the Middle East and in the jurisdictions of India, the United Arab Emirates (UAE), Oman, Kuwait, Qatar, and the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia. DM is the licensed immigration agent with its head office in Dubai, United Arab Emirates.",
