      ".I hereby acknowledge that I have read and fully understood the terms and conditions outlined in the subsequent pages and agree to adhere to the provisions of this Agreement Signature: Page 12 out of 14 pages",
      "Rejection Due to Medical, Criminal, National Security, or Financial Issues: If the Client’s application is rejected on grounds related to medical conditions, criminal records, national security concerns, or financial ineligibility, DM CONSULTANTS shall not issue any refund.",
      "Direct Communication with Authorities: If the Client communicates directly with government bodies, immigration authorities, or any other organizations or agents or employers without the written consent of DM CONSULTANTS, and such communication results in a negative impact on the application process, DM CONSULTANTS shall not be liable to provide any refund.",
      "Provision of False or Fraudulent Information: If the Client is found to have provided false, misleading, or fraudulent documents or engaged in any form of misrepresentation or fraud, DM CONSULTANTS shall not issue any refund.",
      "Completion of Initial Consultation and Document Checklist: Once the Client’s file has been created, the initial consultation has been completed, and the Client has received the required document checklist, the Client agrees that the initial payment is non-refundable, as considerable work has already been invested in processing the Client’s file.",
      "Withdrawal After Agreement Signed: If the Client signs the Agreement and then decides not to proceed with the immigration application for any reason, DM CONSULTANTS will not refund any fees paid up to that point. Dormancy of Client’s File for 90 Days: If the Client's file is dormant for a period of 90 days or more, during which no communication or action is taken by the Client, DM CONSULTANTS reserves the right to close the application temporarily. In such cases, no refund will be applicable.",
      "Client Fails to Complete All Required Procedures: If the Client fails to complete any necessary procedures, steps, or requirements within the time frame stipulated by DM CONSULTANTS or the immigration authorities (such as medical examinations, interviews, etc.), no refund will be granted.",
      ".9 ط‐ اﻟﺮﻓﺾ ﻷﺳﺒﺎب ﻃﺒﻴﺔ أو ﺟﻨﺎﺋﻴﺔ أو ﺗﺘﻌﻠﻖ ﺑﺎﻷﻣﻦ اﻟﻘﻮﻣ أو ﻣﺎﻟﻴﺔ: إذا رﻓﺾ ﻃﻠﺐ اﻟﻌﻤﻴﻞ ﻷﺳﺒﺎب ﺗﺘﻌﻠﻖ ﺑﺎﻟﻈﺮوف اﻟﻄﺒﻴﺔ أو اﻟﺴﺠﻼت اﻟﺠﻨﺎﺋﻴﺔ أو ﻣﺨﺎوف ﺗﺘﻌﻠﻖ ﺑﺎﻷﻣﻦ اﻟﻘﻮﻣ أو ﻋﺪم اﻷﻫﻠﻴﺔ اﻟﻤﺎﻟﻴﺔ، ﻓﻠﻦ ﺗﺮد ﺷﺮﻛﺔ دي إم ﻛﻮﻧﺴﺎﻟﺘﻨﺘﺲ أي أﻣﻮال.",
